-- ============================================================
-- AI Tool Content Update Script - Batch 2 (Tools 51-100)
-- English content_html, natural tone, SEO-safe
-- ============================================================

-- Typefully
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Typefully?</h2><p>If you spend any time building an audience on X (formerly Twitter) or LinkedIn, you know the pain of staring at a blank compose box. Typefully takes that friction away. It gives you a calm, distraction-free writing space with AI that actually helps &mdash; suggesting hook ideas, improving phrasing, and letting you schedule threads for when your audience is most active. Thousands of professional creators swear by it for growing their following.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>The thread composer makes it easy to write long-form Twitter threads with proper formatting. AI writing tools suggest strong opening hooks and help polish your drafts. Smart scheduling publishes posts at peak engagement times, while analytics track impressions and engagement so you can see what works. There is also an auto-retweet feature that resurfaces your best older content.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>There is a free plan with basic scheduling. The Creator plan runs $12.50/month and unlocks AI writing plus advanced analytics. Teams can collaborate on the $29/month plan. Annual billing saves you 20%.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'typefully';

-- ChatGPT
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is ChatGPT?</h2><p>ChatGPT probably needs no introduction at this point. Built by OpenAI and launched in late 2022, it single-handedly kicked off the global AI boom. Powered by GPT-4o, it can hold natural conversations, write essays, analyze spreadsheets, generate images, help you debug code, and a whole lot more. Whether you are a student, marketer, developer, or just curious, chances are ChatGPT has something useful for you.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>GPT-4o delivers state-of-the-art language understanding across dozens of tasks. Web browsing pulls in live information from the internet. DALL-E integration lets you create images from text descriptions right inside the chat. The code interpreter runs Python and crunches data files on the fly. Custom GPTs let anyone build specialized AI assistants, and the advanced voice mode makes conversations feel surprisingly natural.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>The free tier gives you access to GPT-4o mini and basic features. ChatGPT Plus at $20/month unlocks the full GPT-4o model, higher usage limits, and all the premium tools. Teams pay $25/user/month for shared workspaces. There is also an Enterprise tier for large organizations.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'chatgpt';

-- Claude AI
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Claude?</h2><p>Claude is the AI assistant from Anthropic, a safety-focused company founded by former OpenAI researchers. What sets Claude apart is its thoughtful, nuanced writing style and an industry-leading 200K token context window &mdash; meaning you can feed it an entire book or a massive codebase and it will actually process the whole thing. If you care about careful, well-reasoned AI output, Claude deserves a serious look.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>The 200K context window is genuinely game-changing for anyone working with long documents or large code repositories. Constitutional AI training helps the model avoid harmful outputs and stay responsible. Artifacts let you create interactive documents and runnable code snippets visually. Claude is also strong at coding across Python, JavaScript, and many other languages, plus it handles PDF analysis well.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>A free plan gives you limited daily access. Claude Pro at $20/month significantly increases usage limits and offers priority access to the latest models. Claude Team at $25/user/month adds collaboration features for groups.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'claude-ai';

-- Gemini AI
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Gemini?</h2><p>Gemini is Google''s flagship AI assistant, built on their most advanced multimodal models. It used to be called Bard, but Google rebranded it in early 2024 alongside a major upgrade. The biggest draw is how deeply it integrates with the Google ecosystem &mdash; Gmail, Docs, Drive, and more &mdash; making it the natural choice if you already live inside Google''s productivity suite.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>True multimodal understanding means Gemini works with text, images, audio, and video, not just words. Google Search integration keeps answers grounded in current information. The Gemini 1.5 Pro model boasts a 1 million token context window, which is massive. You also get image generation through Imagen, and AI assistance built right into Workspace apps like Docs and Slides.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>The free version gives you Gemini with Search integration. Gemini Advanced at $19.99/month (bundled with Google One AI Premium) unlocks the top-tier model, million-token context, and full Workspace integration.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'gemini-ai';

-- Perplexity AI
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Perplexity AI?</h2><p>Think of Perplexity as Google Search reimagined for the AI era. Instead of handing you a list of blue links, it reads through sources in real-time and gives you a direct, well-sourced answer with citations you can verify. For researchers, students, and anyone who needs reliable, current information fast, it has quickly become indispensable.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Every answer is backed by real-time web sources with inline citations, so you can check the original pages yourself. Pro users get to choose between multiple frontier models including GPT-4o, Claude 3, and Gemini. Spaces let you organize research into shareable collections. Image search and analysis round out the toolkit for visual queries.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>The free plan includes a limited number of Pro searches per day. Perplexity Pro at $20/month delivers unlimited Pro searches, access to all premium models, and higher file upload limits.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'perplexity-ai';

-- Microsoft Copilot
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Microsoft Copilot?</h2><p>Microsoft took its partnership with OpenAI and baked GPT-4o directly into Windows 11, Edge, and the entire Microsoft 365 suite. The result is Copilot &mdash; an AI assistant that lives where you already work. For anyone using Outlook, Teams, Excel, or Word daily, the productivity gains can be substantial. And the basic version is completely free.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>The core experience combines GPT-4o chat with Bing search for real-time, grounded answers. DALL-E 3 is built in for image generation from text. Where Copilot really shines is inside Microsoft 365: drafting Outlook emails, summarizing Teams meetings, analyzing Excel data, and creating PowerPoint decks from natural language prompts. Windows 11 integration means AI help is always one keystroke away.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Basic Copilot is free for Windows and Edge users. Microsoft 365 subscribers get Copilot features inside their apps. The full business tier costs $30/user/month and covers deep integration across every M365 app.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'microsoft-copilot';

-- Mistral Chat
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Mistral Chat?</h2><p>Mistral AI, based in Paris, has been making waves by releasing open-weight models that punch well above their size class. Their chat interface, Le Chat, lets anyone try these models for free. If you care about European data privacy standards or want a powerful model you can self-host, Mistral is one of the most interesting players in the AI space right now.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Mistral Large handles complex reasoning at a level competitive with GPT-4, while Mistral Small is optimized for speed and efficiency. Open-weight models can be self-hosted, which matters a lot for companies that need to keep data in-house. Function calling and JSON mode make it developer-friendly. Multilingual support is strong, especially for European languages.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Le Chat is free for anyone on the web. API access is billed per token, with Mistral Small being very affordable. A Pro subscription at about $15/month offers higher limits and priority access to the latest models.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'mistral-chat';

-- Llama Chat / Meta AI
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Meta AI?</h2><p>Meta AI is the assistant powered by Meta''s Llama family of large language models. What makes it unique is where it lives: directly inside WhatsApp, Instagram, Facebook, and Messenger. Billions of people can use AI without downloading a new app or creating a new account. You just chat with it like you would a friend.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Ask Meta AI questions, get help with tasks, and generate images, all within the social apps you already use daily. Real-time search keeps answers current. The underlying Llama models are open-source, which has made them hugely popular in the research and developer community. You can even summon Meta AI in group chats to help everyone at once.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Meta AI is completely free. No subscription, no hidden costs. If you use any Meta platform, you already have access.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'llama-chat';

-- Poe
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Poe?</h2><p>Built by Quora, Poe solves a real problem: instead of subscribing separately to ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini, and others, you get access to all of them in one app. Switch between GPT-4o, Claude 3.5, Gemini, Llama, and more, picking the best model for each task without juggling multiple subscriptions.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Over 20 frontier AI models are available in a single interface. You can build custom bots using just prompts with no coding needed, and share them on a bot marketplace. Multi-turn memory keeps context across long conversations. Native iOS and Android apps make everything mobile-friendly.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Free users get limited messages with each model. Poe Premium at $19.99/month provides 1 million points per month, which goes a long way. Annual billing offers a discount.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'poe';

-- Character AI
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Character AI?</h2><p>Character AI is not your typical productivity assistant. Founded by former Google Brain researchers, it is built for immersive conversation with AI characters &mdash; celebrities, historical figures, anime heroes, or personas you create yourself. It has found a massive audience among younger users who use it for creative roleplay, language practice, and entertainment.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Millions of user-created characters span everything from anime and gaming to historical figures and fictional worlds. Creating your own character is straightforward and requires no coding. Group chat lets you talk with multiple AI characters at once. Voice mode enables actual spoken conversations, making interactions feel surprisingly personal.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Most features are free, though wait times can occur during peak hours. Character AI Plus at $9.99/month skips the queue, delivers faster responses, and grants early access to new features.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'character-ai';

-- Pi AI
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Pi?</h2><p>Pi, short for Personal Intelligence, is an AI companion from Inflection AI. Co-founded by LinkedIn co-founder Reid Hoffman and DeepMind co-founder Mustafa Suleyman, Pi takes a different approach than most chatbots. Rather than maximizing raw information retrieval, it focuses on emotional intelligence, empathy, and being genuinely supportive in conversation. It feels less like a search engine and more like a thoughtful friend.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Pi has a warm, natural conversational style that avoids the robotic tone many chatbots fall into. Multiple voice personas are available for spoken conversations. A personal memory feature lets Pi remember past chats and build on them. It even checks in on you proactively. Available across web, iOS, and Android with a seamless experience.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Pi is currently free with no ads or subscription required. Inflection AI generates revenue through enterprise products separate from the consumer Pi service.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'pi-ai';

-- You.com
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is You.com?</h2><p>You.com positions itself as an AI-powered alternative to Google that respects your privacy. It combines web search with a suite of specialized AI tools for chatting, coding, writing, and image generation, all in one place. If you want one platform that does many things well without tracking your every click, this is worth checking out.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>YouChat provides AI conversations with real-time web citations. YouCode specializes in programming and code generation. YouWrite handles emails, blog posts, and marketing copy. YouImagine creates images from text descriptions. The platform is privacy-first and does not store personal search data. Different AI modes let you pick the right tool for the job.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>The basic plan is free with daily usage limits across all modes. YouPro at $15/month unlocks unlimited usage, premium model responses, and access to all advanced features.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'you-com';

-- Phind
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Phind?</h2><p>Phind is an AI search engine built specifically for software developers. Instead of generic answers, it searches through technical documentation, Stack Overflow threads, GitHub repos, and developer blogs, then synthesizes everything into a clear, code-ready answer. If you are a developer who is tired of wading through irrelevant search results, Phind feels like a breath of fresh air.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Developer-focused search pulls from the right technical sources. The Phind-70B model delivers AI reasoning tuned specifically for code. A VS Code extension lets you use Phind without leaving your editor. Answers include working code examples alongside clear explanations, and every claim links back to original documentation or discussions. Pair programming mode supports interactive debugging sessions.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>The free plan provides daily searches using the Phind-34B model. Phind Pro at $17/month unlocks Phind-70B and GPT-4o for unlimited searches with faster response times.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'phind';

-- Bing Chat
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Bing Chat?</h2><p>Bing Chat is Microsoft''s AI chat assistant integrated into the Bing search engine and Edge browser. Powered by GPT-4o and connected to Bing''s live web index, it blends the traditional search experience with cited, conversational AI answers. It has since been folded into the Microsoft Copilot brand, but the free access remains.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Every response includes real-time Bing web results with source citations. GPT-4o powers natural conversation on any topic. DALL-E 3 is integrated for free image generation from text descriptions. Three conversation styles &mdash; Creative, Balanced, and Precise &mdash; let you control the tone. Deep Edge integration means you can get AI help while browsing any website.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Bing Chat is free within daily usage limits. All you need is a Microsoft account to access it through Bing.com, the Edge sidebar, or the Copilot app.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'bing-chat';

-- Bard AI
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Bard AI?</h2><p>Bard was Google''s conversational AI assistant launched in March 2023 to compete with ChatGPT. It was powered by Google''s LaMDA and later PaLM 2 language models, combining conversational AI with Google Search capabilities. In February 2024, Google rebranded Bard as Gemini, aligning it with their latest model family.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Bard offered real-time Google Search integration, multiple response drafts for each query, export to Google Docs and Gmail, and image understanding through Google Lens. All of these capabilities have been carried forward and improved in Gemini, its successor.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Bard was free and only required a Google account. Gemini continues to offer a free tier, with Gemini Advanced available as a paid upgrade for more powerful capabilities.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'bard-ai';

-- OpenAI Playground
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is OpenAI Playground?</h2><p>The OpenAI Playground is a web-based sandbox where developers and researchers can experiment directly with OpenAI''s full model lineup, including GPT-4o, GPT-4 Turbo, and o1-mini. It is the go-to place for testing prompts, tuning parameters, and exploring model behavior before building anything into production.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>You get access to every current OpenAI model. Full control over parameters like temperature, max tokens, and frequency penalty lets you fine-tune outputs precisely. System prompts define how the AI behaves. A comparison mode shows results from multiple models side by side. Fine-tuning with your own data and testing the Assistants API are also supported.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>The Playground itself is free to access, but you need an OpenAI account with API credits. Costs are based on token usage (e.g., GPT-4o input is about $5 per million tokens). New accounts sometimes receive free starter credits.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'openai-playground';

-- Stable Diffusion
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Stable Diffusion?</h2><p>Stable Diffusion, released by Stability AI in 2022, changed the game by being the first high-quality image generation model you could download and run entirely on your own hardware. No cloud service, no per-image fees, no data leaving your machine. For hobbyists, artists, and developers who want complete control, it remains the most flexible option available.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Beyond basic text-to-image generation, it supports image-to-image transformation, inpainting, and outpainting. ControlNet extensions let you guide generation with poses and edge maps for precise results. Thousands of community-created fine-tuned models (checkpoints) and LoRA adapters cover virtually every art style you can imagine.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>The base model is free to download and run. Cloud interfaces like Stability AI''s DreamStudio charge credits per generation. Third-party local UIs like AUTOMATIC1111 and ComfyUI are free and open-source.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'stable-diffusion';

-- Adobe Firefly
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Adobe Firefly?</h2><p>Adobe Firefly is Adobe''s generative AI toolkit, baked directly into Photoshop, Illustrator, and Adobe Express. The standout differentiator is how it was trained: exclusively on licensed content and public domain material. That means you can use Firefly-generated assets in commercial projects without the copyright anxiety that plagues other AI image tools.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Generative Fill and Generative Expand in Photoshop let you seamlessly remove objects or extend a canvas with AI-generated content that matches the scene. Illustrator gets generative recoloring and shape tools for vectors. The web app supports text effects and text-to-image generation with style reference capabilities.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Firefly is included with all paid Adobe Creative Cloud plans, each providing monthly generative credits. Free users can try the web version with limited credits. A standalone Firefly subscription is also available.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'adobe-firefly';

-- Canva AI
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Canva AI?</h2><p>Canva AI refers to the growing suite of artificial intelligence features inside Canva, the hugely popular online design platform. The centerpiece is Magic Media, an AI image generator that creates visuals from text prompts. What makes it practical is the integration: generate an image and drop it straight into any of Canva''s thousands of templates for instant design work.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Magic Media generates images in styles ranging from photorealistic to watercolor to animation. Magic Edit lets you select any object in a photo, describe a change in words, and watch the AI make it happen. Background Remover and Magic Eraser automate tedious photo editing tasks with one click.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Free Canva users get a limited number of Magic Media generations per month. Canva Pro at $14.99/month unlocks 500 monthly AI generations, all Magic features, and unlimited premium template access.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'canva-ai';

-- Leonardo AI
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Leonardo AI?</h2><p>Leonardo AI is a professional-grade image generation platform built with game developers and digital artists in mind. It offers a curated library of fine-tuned models optimized for specific art styles and use cases, making it easier to produce consistent, high-quality visuals at scale compared to more general-purpose tools.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Real-Time Canvas lets you sketch while watching the AI transform your strokes into finished artwork in real time. ControlNet support gives you precise control over poses and composition. Motion generation brings still images to life. The standout feature is custom model training, allowing studios to create proprietary style assets at volume.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Free users get 150 tokens daily. Paid plans start at $12/month (Artisan) with 8,500 monthly tokens. Higher tiers offer more tokens, faster generation, and private generation capabilities.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'leonardo-ai';

-- Ideogram
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Ideogram?</h2><p>Founded by former Google Brain researchers in 2023, Ideogram tackled one of AI image generation''s hardest problems: rendering readable text inside images. If you have ever tried to generate a logo, poster, or social media graphic with AI and gotten garbled letters, you understand why this matters. Ideogram consistently produces clean, accurate typography that other tools still struggle with.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Text rendering accuracy is the headline feature &mdash; the words you type actually appear correctly in the generated image. Magic Prompt automatically expands short inputs into detailed prompts for better results. Style references let you guide the visual direction. Multiple aspect ratios are supported out of the box.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>A free plan lets you generate a limited number of images daily. Paid plans start at $8/month (Basic) and include priority queue, private generations, and higher output limits.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'ideogram';

-- Playground AI
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Playground AI?</h2><p>Playground (formerly Playground AI) is a web-based creative platform where you can generate, edit, and composite images. It goes beyond simple generation by offering an infinite canvas interface where you can arrange multiple images, make edits, and build complete compositions in one workspace.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Both Stable Diffusion and Playground''s own v3 model are supported. The infinite canvas lets you work with layers, erase unwanted elements with Magic Eraser, or swap backgrounds. Real-time collaboration lets multiple users work together. Image Mixing blends styles in creative ways.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>One of the most generous free tiers in the industry: up to 500 images per day. The Pro plan at $15/month adds faster generation, high-quality upscaling, and permanent private mode.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'playground-ai';

-- NightCafe
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is NightCafe?</h2><p>NightCafe Creator has been around since 2019, making it one of the earliest AI art platforms. What keeps it relevant is the combination of multiple generation engines and a vibrant social community. You can use Stable Diffusion, DALL-E 3, VQGAN+CLIP, and more, all in one place, trying out different models on the same prompt to see what you like best.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Switch between major AI models on a single platform. Daily themed art challenges let you compete with and vote alongside other creators. Style Transfer converts your photos into paintings in the style of famous artists. Print-on-demand integration means you can put your creations on merchandise.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Five free credits daily, plus you can earn more through community engagement. Paid subscriptions start at $9.99/month for additional credits, an ad-free experience, and faster generation.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'nightcafe';

-- BlueWillow
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is BlueWillow?</h2><p>BlueWillow is a free AI image generator that operates through Discord, similar in feel to Midjourney. It gained early popularity as a no-cost alternative, combining several open-source models behind the scenes so anyone can create artistic images without paying a subscription or understanding prompt engineering.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Type the /imagine command in Discord to generate images. Photorealistic, fantasy, anime, oil painting, and many other styles are available through text prompts. Upscaling and variation tools let you refine outputs. The low barrier to entry makes it great for beginners exploring AI art for the first time.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>BlueWillow is currently free. Join the Discord server and you can generate images without any payment. Policies may change in the future as the service evolves.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'bluewillow';

-- Bing Image Creator
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Bing Image Creator?</h2><p>Bing Image Creator is Microsoft''s free AI image generator, powered by OpenAI''s DALL-E 3. It is woven into the Bing search engine, Edge browser, Microsoft Designer, and Copilot, so you can generate high-quality images without leaving the tools you already use for browsing and productivity.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>DALL-E 3 delivers strong prompt comprehension and handles both photorealistic and artistic styles well. Boost credits, tied to Microsoft Rewards, prioritize your generations for faster results. Save images to collections, share directly, or send them to Microsoft Designer for further editing.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Completely free with a Microsoft account. Daily boost credits are provided for fast generation. When boosts run out, images still generate &mdash; just a bit slower.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'bing-image-creator';

-- Getimg.ai
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Getimg.ai?</h2><p>Getimg.ai packs over 60 AI models into a single platform, making it an all-in-one toolkit for image generation and editing. It caters to everyone from casual users to professionals who want granular control, including the ability to train custom AI models on your own images.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Over 60 models are available instantly, including various Stable Diffusion versions and community fine-tunes. Custom model training (LoRA) lets you create AI that generates in your specific style. An infinite canvas editor supports inpainting and outpainting. ControlNet integration gives precise control over the generation process.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>The free plan includes 100 monthly image generations. Paid plans start at $12/month with 3,000+ monthly generations, custom model training, and priority processing.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'getimg-ai';

-- DreamStudio
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is DreamStudio?</h2><p>DreamStudio is the official web interface built by Stability AI, the company behind Stable Diffusion. It gives you browser-based access to their latest models &mdash; including Stable Diffusion 3, SDXL, and Stable Image Ultra &mdash; without needing a powerful GPU on your own machine.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>First access to Stability AI''s newest models. Fine-grained control over aspect ratios, generation steps, CFG scale, seed values, and other professional settings. Inpainting and outpainting tools are included. Generation history management and API key administration are built in for developers.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Pay-as-you-go credit system rather than a subscription. $10 gets you 1,000 credits, with costs per image varying by model and settings. New signups receive 25 free credits to start.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'dreamstudio';

-- Dream by Wombo
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Dream by Wombo?</h2><p>Dream by Wombo is a mobile-first AI art app from Canadian startup Wombo AI. Launched in 2021, it was one of the earliest apps to bring AI art creation to a mainstream audience. Its appeal is simplicity: pick a style filter, type a few words, and get fantastical artwork without any prompt engineering expertise.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Dozens of unique art style filters like Ghibli, cyberpunk, and oil painting make it easy for anyone to create visually striking images. The mobile-optimized interface is extremely intuitive. Reference images can guide composition. Community features and NFT minting are also available within the app.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>The free version has limited styles and adds a watermark. Premium at $9.99/month unlocks all styles, higher resolution output, watermark removal, and an ad-free experience.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'dream-by-wombo';

-- StarryAI
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is StarryAI?</h2><p>StarryAI takes a clear stance on ownership: every image you create belongs entirely to you. No watermarks, full commercial rights, full creative freedom. This makes it popular among artists who want to mint NFTs, sell prints, or use AI art in commercial projects without worrying about licensing restrictions.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Two AI engines serve different needs: Altair produces abstract, dreamlike pieces, while Orion generates more realistic and detailed images. Available on both mobile and web. You can create art using text prompts or even emojis. Canvas tools allow post-generation editing and upscaling.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Five free credits daily (enough for five images). Pro subscriptions start at $11.99/month with 50+ monthly credits, faster generation, no ads, and unlimited canvas tool access.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'starryai';

-- Fotor AI
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Fotor AI?</h2><p>Fotor AI adds generative AI capabilities to the established Fotor online photo editing platform. The real strength is the workflow: generate an image from text, then immediately edit, enhance, and design with it using Fotor''s full editing suite &mdash; all without switching apps.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Text-to-image generation flows into a full photo editor. AI background removal, image enhancement, and object eraser tools are all available alongside the generator. Tens of thousands of design templates, stickers, and fonts make it easy to turn generated images into polished social media posts, posters, and banners.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Free users receive limited AI generation credits. Fotor Pro at $8.99/month and Pro+ offer generous monthly credits, watermark-free high-resolution downloads, and access to all premium editing features.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'fotor-ai';

-- Pixlr AI
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Pixlr AI?</h2><p>Pixlr has been a trusted online photo editor since 2008, and its AI features bring generative capabilities to that familiar environment. Generate images from text right in your browser, then edit them using Pixlr''s professional layer-based editor. It also offers a Generative Fill feature similar to what you would find in Photoshop.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Pixlr Editor provides professional photo editing with layers, masks, and blending modes, now combined with AI generation tools. Generative Fill lets you modify specific parts of an image with AI. Background removal and image enhancement are also AI-powered.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>The free version includes ads and feature limitations. Pixlr Plus at $1.99/month and Premium at $7.99/month provide ad-free access, unlimited AI generations, and all advanced editing tools.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'pixlr-ai';

-- Photosonic
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Photosonic?</h2><p>Photosonic is the AI image generator built by Writesonic, the popular AI writing platform. It is designed for bloggers and content marketers who want to create matching visuals right alongside their written content. Built on Stable Diffusion, it integrates directly with Writesonic''s writing tools for a streamlined content creation workflow.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Tight integration with Writesonic speeds up the content production pipeline. Generate high-quality images in various artistic styles from text prompts. Face enhancement helps produce better portrait images. All generated images come with commercial use rights.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Photosonic is included with Writesonic paid plans. A free trial provides limited credits for testing. Paid plans start at $19/month.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'photosonic';

-- Jasper Art
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Jasper Art?</h2><p>Jasper Art is the image generation feature within Jasper, the enterprise marketing AI platform. It is purpose-built for marketing teams who need original visuals for campaigns, blog posts, and social media without relying on stock photos. The focus is on brand consistency and speed for professional content production.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Direct integration with Jasper''s document editor means you can write and generate images in the same session. Marketing-optimized style presets produce commercially polished results. High-quality outputs work as stock photo replacements. Team collaboration features let everyone share and manage brand assets.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Jasper Art is bundled with Jasper Creator ($39/month) and Pro ($59/month) plans. Unlimited image generation is included at no additional cost, making it economical for teams with heavy image needs.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'jasper-art';

-- Stockimg.ai
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Stockimg.ai?</h2><p>Stockimg.ai is laser-focused on generating images for practical business use. Rather than general-purpose art generation, its models are optimized for specific commercial categories: stock photos, logos, book covers, posters, UI/UX designs, and wallpapers. The results tend to be more immediately usable in professional contexts.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Specialized generation modes for different use cases (book covers, logos, posters, etc.) produce more targeted results than generic models. High-resolution output is supported. All generated images come with commercial licensing. The interface is designed to be accessible even for people without any design background.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>A free trial allows limited generations. Paid plans start at $19/month with commercial licenses, more generation credits, fast processing, and upscaling capabilities.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'stockimg-ai';

-- Krita AI
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Krita AI?</h2><p>Krita AI typically refers to the Krita AI Diffusion plugin, which brings Stable Diffusion directly into Krita, the free open-source digital painting program. This means artists can run AI generation locally on their own GPU, transforming sketches into polished illustrations or getting real-time AI assistance as they paint, all within their existing creative workflow.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Krita''s professional painting tools integrate with AI generation at the layer level. Live painting mode shows AI-completed results as you draw in real time. Inpainting, outpainting, and sketch enhancement all run on your local GPU, making them free and unlimited to use.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Both Krita and the AI plugin are completely free. However, you do need a capable NVIDIA GPU to run the AI features smoothly.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'krita-ai';

-- Google Imagen
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Google Imagen?</h2><p>Google Imagen is a state-of-the-art text-to-image diffusion model developed by Google DeepMind and Research. It is recognized for industry-leading photorealism and an exceptional ability to follow complex prompts accurately. Imagen 3 is the latest version and serves as the backbone for image generation across multiple Google services.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Photorealistic quality and accurate text rendering are standout capabilities. Imagen is integrated into Google Gemini, Google Workspace (Docs, Slides), and Google Cloud Vertex AI. Enterprise-grade reliability and safety guardrails make it suitable for business applications.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Consumer access is through Gemini Advanced at $19.99/month (Google One AI Premium). Developers and businesses can use Imagen via the Google Cloud Vertex AI API on a pay-per-use basis.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'imagen-google';

-- Microsoft Designer
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Microsoft Designer?</h2><p>Microsoft Designer is an AI-powered graphic design app that uses DALL-E 3 under the hood. Describe what you want in plain language and it generates not just images, but complete design layouts for invitations, posters, social media posts, and more. It is designed to give non-designers professional-looking results with minimal effort.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>DALL-E 3 powers high-quality image generation. AI-driven layout suggestions, background removal and blur, and brand kit application streamline the entire design process. Integration with Microsoft 365 apps and Copilot makes it easy to access. The tool is approachable enough for complete beginners to produce polished results.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Currently free with a Microsoft account (preview period). Some features may eventually move behind a Microsoft 365 subscription.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'designer-microsoft';

-- PicsArt AI
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is PicsArt AI?</h2><p>PicsArt AI is the AI feature suite within PicsArt, a mobile photo editing and creation platform used by over 150 million people. It is optimized for mobile and geared toward social media content, offering trendy tools like AI avatars, background swaps, and image enhancement alongside a traditional text-to-image generator.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>AI Avatars transform selfies into stylized artistic portraits and are hugely popular. Text-to-image generation, AI object eraser, and image upscaling round out the editing toolkit. A massive library of stickers, fonts, and effects makes creative customization easy.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>The free app provides limited AI features. PicsArt Gold at $11.99/month unlocks unlimited AI tools, premium content, and removes ads.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'picsart-ai';

-- ElevenLabs
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is ElevenLabs?</h2><p>ElevenLabs has pushed AI voice synthesis to a level where generated speech is nearly indistinguishable from real human recordings. Using deep learning, it captures emotion, intonation, and even breathing patterns. The voice cloning feature is particularly impressive: just one minute of audio is enough to create a realistic replica of anyone''s voice.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Text-to-speech covers 29 languages with remarkably natural output. Voice Design lets you create entirely new voices from scratch. Instant Voice Cloning reproduces a real person''s voice from a short sample. The technology is used across audiobook production, game character voices, video dubbing, and more.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>The free plan provides 10,000 characters/month (roughly 10 minutes of audio). Starter at $5/month unlocks voice cloning. Creator at $22/month offers 100,000 characters for more serious production work.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'elevenlabs';

-- Murf AI
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Murf AI?</h2><p>Murf AI is a professional voiceover platform built for corporate training, marketing videos, and e-learning content. With over 120 AI voices spanning different ages and tones, it goes beyond basic text-to-speech by providing a studio environment where you can edit voice tracks, sync them with video or presentation slides, and fine-tune the delivery.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>A large library of professional-grade voices suited for corporate content. The built-in video editor lets you add voiceovers directly to footage and sync timing. Pitch, speed, and emphasis controls help you dial in natural-sounding delivery. Team collaboration features support enterprise workflows.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>A free trial lets you test the platform. The Basic plan at $19/month covers core voice generation and downloads. Pro at $26/month adds premium voices, voice cloning, and commercial use rights.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'murf-ai';

-- Midjourney
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Midjourney?</h2><p>Midjourney is widely considered the gold standard for AI-generated art. It produces images with a painterly, almost cinematic quality that other generators have struggled to match. The workflow is unique: everything happens through Discord, where you type prompts into a chat channel and the AI delivers results in seconds. Millions of creatives worldwide rely on it as their primary AI art tool.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>The artistic quality and level of detail are the main attraction. Discord-based commands (/imagine) drive the whole workflow. Zoom Out (outpainting), Pan (extending images in any direction), Remix mode, and Style Tuner give you extensive creative control. The community aspect is strong too &mdash; you can see other people''s prompts and results for inspiration.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>No free trial is currently available. Basic starts at $10/month. Standard at $30/month and above add fast generation time and private mode (Pro tier and up).</p>'
WHERE slug = 'midjourney';

-- Descript
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Descript?</h2><p>Descript changes how you think about audio and video editing. Instead of working with timelines and waveforms, you edit a transcript. Delete a sentence from the text, and the corresponding audio or video clip disappears. It is like editing a Word document, except the result is a finished podcast episode or YouTube video. For podcasters, video creators, and anyone editing interviews, it removes a massive amount of friction.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Transcript-based editing is the core innovation. Overdub lets you type words and hear them in your own AI-cloned voice, perfect for fixing mistakes without re-recording. Studio Sound removes background noise and enhances audio to near-studio quality. Automatic captions, screen recording, and Eye Contact correction are also included.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>The free plan includes 1 hour/month of transcription and exports. Creator at $12/month and Pro at $24/month provide unlimited editing, watermark removal, and 10-30 hours of monthly transcription.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'descript';

-- Udio AI
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Udio?</h2><p>Developed by former Google DeepMind researchers, Udio is one of the most talked-about AI music generators right now. From a simple text prompt, it creates full songs complete with vocals, lyrics, and instrumentation. The musical coherence and vocal quality are remarkably high, and it handles everything from classical to pop to jazz with impressive range.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Generate complete songs over 3 minutes long from text descriptions. Write your own lyrics or let the AI handle them. Extend tracks by adding intro or outro sections, or remix specific parts. The output audio quality rivals professionally produced demos.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Currently free during the beta period, with generous daily credits for up to 600 generations. Paid plans are expected in the future, but for now it remains one of the most generous free offerings in AI music.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'udio-ai';

-- Suno AI
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Suno AI?</h2><p>Suno brings music creation to everyone, regardless of musical training. Type a description of the song you want &mdash; genre, mood, topic &mdash; and within a couple of minutes, you get a complete track with lyrics, vocals, and backing instruments. Available through its website and integrated with Microsoft Copilot, Suno has done more than perhaps any other tool to democratize music creation.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>The V3 model produces radio-quality songs up to 2 minutes long. Custom Mode lets you specify exact lyrics, musical style, and title for more precise results. Songs can be downloaded as video for easy social media sharing. Paid subscribers own the copyright to their generated tracks.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>The free plan gives 50 daily credits (about 10 songs). Pro at $8/month and Premier at $24/month add commercial use rights and 2,500-10,000 monthly credits for serious output volume.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'suno-ai';

-- AIVA
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is AIVA?</h2><p>AIVA (Artificial Intelligence Virtual Artist) specializes in composing classical, film, and game soundtrack music. Unlike most AI music tools that only output finished audio files, AIVA lets you download MIDI files so you can edit the composition in your own DAW &mdash; swap instruments, tweak melodies, adjust arrangements. That flexibility is what makes it valuable for working composers and producers.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Composes across a wide range of styles, from intimate piano solos to grand orchestral symphonies. Upload existing tracks for style reference, or specify tempo, time signature, and key to guide new compositions. MIDI export is the killer feature for musicians who want to use AI as a creative starting point rather than a final product.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>The free plan is non-commercial only and requires AIVA attribution. Standard at about $11/month and Pro at about $33/month unlock commercial rights. Pro users own the full copyright to generated compositions.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'aiva';

-- Soundraw
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Soundraw?</h2><p>Soundraw is a royalty-free AI music generator designed for video creators, podcasters, and streamers. It takes the pain out of hunting for background music by letting you customize tracks to fit your content''s length and mood perfectly. Think of it as a BGM vending machine that creates unique tracks on demand.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Select mood, genre, theme, length, and tempo, and Soundraw generates dozens of candidate tracks. Each track''s structure can be rearranged with clicks &mdash; swap sections, adjust energy levels, match your video''s pacing exactly. A permanent license means even if you cancel your subscription, music you have already used stays cleared.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>You can generate and preview music for free. Downloads and commercial use (YouTube, etc.) require the Creator plan at $16.99/month.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'soundraw';

-- Beatoven.ai
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Beatoven.ai?</h2><p>Beatoven.ai generates royalty-free background music for YouTubers, podcasters, and indie game developers. It uses advanced AI to compose original tracks based on your chosen genre and emotional arc. The standout feature is segment-level emotion control: set different moods for different parts of a single track, and the AI smoothly transitions between them.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Divide a track into segments and assign different emotions (joy, sadness, tension) to each one. Multiple genres (indie, pop, ambient) and instrument configurations are supported. A drag-and-drop interface makes editing intuitive. All generated music is royalty-free, so there are no copyright strikes to worry about.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Music generation and editing are free and unlimited. Downloading finished tracks requires a subscription, with pricing based on usage (starting around $6/month).</p>'
WHERE slug = 'beatoven-ai';

-- LALAL.AI
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is LALAL.AI?</h2><p>LALAL.AI is the go-to service for audio stem separation. It goes far beyond basic vocal removal: you can isolate drums, bass, piano, electric guitar, acoustic guitar, synths, and more from any track with impressive accuracy. DJs use it for remixes, musicians use it for practice tracks, and producers use it for sampling &mdash; it is an essential tool for anyone working with audio.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>The Phoenix algorithm delivers industry-leading separation accuracy. Up to 10 individual stems can be extracted from a single track. It processes both audio and video files. A noise cancellation mode can clean up recorded speech by removing background noise.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Free previews of up to 10 minutes. Instead of subscriptions, you buy minute-based packs. The Starter pack (90 minutes) costs about $15, with larger packs available at better per-minute rates.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'lalal-ai';

-- Riffusion
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Riffusion?</h2><p>Riffusion takes a genuinely novel approach to music generation. It applies Stable Diffusion''s image generation techniques to spectrograms &mdash; visual representations of sound &mdash; and then converts the generated spectrograms back into audio. The result is an experimental but fascinating pathway to AI-created music, and it is entirely open-source.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Spectrogram-based music generation from text prompts. Style interpolation smoothly transitions between different musical genres or moods. Loop creation is supported. The entire project is free and open-source, available for local deployment.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Completely free on the web with no limits and no account required. The code and model weights are open-source for anyone who wants to run it locally.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'riffusion';

-- Adobe Podcast
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Adobe Podcast?</h2><p>Adobe Podcast (formerly Project Shasta) is Adobe''s AI audio toolkit for podcasters and audio content creators. Its standout feature, Enhance Speech, can take a recording made on a laptop mic in a noisy room and make it sound like it was captured in a professional studio. For anyone producing audio content on a budget, that alone makes it worth trying.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Enhance Speech dramatically improves recording quality by removing noise, echo, and mic artifacts. Mic Check gives real-time feedback on your recording setup before you start. Transcript-based editing lets you cut audio by editing text. Web-based recording is also built in.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Enhance Speech and some tools are free with no account required. Full platform access comes with Adobe Creative Cloud subscriptions starting at $19.99/month.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'adobe-podcast';
